{"tid":2413223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荷蘭孔子學院被揭發要脅教授「教學研究違反中国法律或損害中國形象可被解僱」 議員炮轟違反學術自由","createTime":"2021-02-18T14:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T16:03:17.000Z","uid":63183,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4f367c418da01712e627a3001ca53eba0592a0e8","tid":2413223,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvNziWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzvNziWm.png&h=bf9aaeb7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5306&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69PcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=24922245\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5306</a><br />\n早前喺荷蘭，香港留學生聯署請願，要求格羅寧根大學（University of Groningen ）同孔子學院解除合約，引起當地關注。近日孔子學院就被踢爆，同教職員簽嘅合約竟然要脅話「教學研究違反中国法律或損害中國形象可被解僱」 ，被議員炮轟違反學術自由。荷蘭教育部揚言定必跟進，「不容討價還價」。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒搵到份由孔子學院出部分人工嘅教授合約，合約寫明禁止教授損害中國形象，如果教授嘅教學同研究「嚴重違反中国法律或嚴重損害中国形象」，中方可以單方面終止任用該為教授，仲要中国教育部直屬嘅国家漢語國際推廣領導小組辦公室（漢辦）有權決定幾時炒人。<br />\n<br />\n教育部部長范安高蘇芬（Van Engelshoven）表示非常關注，會盡快同格羅寧根大學會面。「每間大學都有法律責任去保障學術自由，呢樣嘢係冇得討價還價。我諗大學要遵守呢啲法律責任。」佢哋都會研究呢種合同係咪違反咗荷蘭嘅勞工法例。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭眾議院議員促請教育部部長盡快徹查，議員范美蘭（Van Meenen）話：「（中国）如果用呢種方式影響我哋嘅教育，真係不可接受。」<br />\n<br />\n范希佛（Van Helvert）議員就認為，呢單嘢表現咗「中国點樣透過海外国民去用唔正當嘅方式獲取情報，同埋點樣嚴密限制學術自由。」佢認為學生都受到監視， 「好似監視啲維吾爾人咁。」<br />\n<br />\n喺格大嘅香港學生早前發起聯署，呼籲大學唔好再同中国孔子學院合作，因為中国透過緊呢樣嘢干預師生。<br />\n<br />\n發起聯署嘅香港學生為咗保障人身安全，唯有匿名。佢哋接受港語學訪問時話，支持荷蘭政府採取行動，保障學術自由，亦都要求大學公開交代：「唔好再官腔講we are not aware of any issues 咁。」<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭而家有兩間孔子學院，喺格羅寧根同馬斯垂克。萊頓大學喺2019年終止咗孔子學院嘅所有合作。由於喺多國都有報道，中国利用呢啲做情報間諜工作，喺美國、比利時已經踢走咗好多間孔子學院。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道（荷蘭傳媒NOS、港語學獨家訪問）"},{"pid":"8063c05176f5f611a3cb2081df07bbf30b860e01","tid":2413223,"uid":63183,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>重點：香港留學生發起聯署引起當地關注</strong><br />\n聯署係有用"},{"pid":"8d689ee62a3d495490a40974861c28d88f9f8669","tid":2413223,"uid":232949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fca5f88d4e9bd745e2faf86e6bf6114917f215","tid":2413223,"uid":295459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收哂班垃圾孔子學院皮"},{"pid":"f79906c10030cd3245fba2a08a16664a50444bd7","tid":2413223,"uid":292987,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:15:18.000Z","msg":"孔子學院=漢辦 點解仲要發現新大陸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af06c1052276478aed846b1d65e818865b71e1b5","tid":2413223,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437375c51fa1a78e17df1479ae4cbfa8631bf419","tid":2413223,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHm0ZyT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHm0ZyT.gif&h=9313de99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7a5f75aaa9fc334591701e96bf35dee8dd694a8","tid":2413223,"uid":47080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"根本就係間諜洗腦中心<br />\n封咗全球孔子學院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767412147ce3d100e3828a08d961477fcf77bd90","tid":2413223,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f846fac643ed33396889a7b92c803e9113f76e7","tid":2413223,"uid":103146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8063c05176f5f611a3cb2081df07bbf30b860e01","tid":2413223,"uid":63183,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>重點：香港留學生發起聯署引起當地關注</strong><br />\n聯署係有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:57:36.000Z","msg":"聯署喺文明世界有效好多<br />\n（當然follow up，聯繫關注團體都好緊要"},{"pid":"c6454b21cab92d7556c53f7bc80ddf2a616dedc3","tid":2413223,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32743964ebda5a78dff2b7a6922ad211b430c4d7","tid":2413223,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:03:17.000Z","msg":"荷蘭都要守中國法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}